Package com.openclassrooms.tourguide.model

Class User

java.lang.Object
com.openclassrooms.tourguide.model.User
public class User extends Object
A model class which creates the POJO (Plain Old Java Object) User. It contains getters and setters, as well as an override toSring() method for display in the console.
Version:
1.1
Author:
[NPC]TourGuide BackEnd Team, SÃ©bastien Cappon
Singularity :
addUserReward method has been modified to manage the multithreading induced by the getAttraction() method of the GpsUtil module, without creating a list of temporary rewards, when it is called in the calculateRewards() method of the RewardService class.
